    "title": "Khadim's is Hiring: Floor Manager (Principal)",
    "description": "Grow your career with Khadim's! We are hiring a Floor Manager for our Amritsar team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Khadim's:\nKhadim's is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in Category Management\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Learning & development budget\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Amritsar, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Khadim's!",
